name: Eyeglasses Contacts Discount Eyewear Superstore
overview: Eyeglasses Contacts, Inc offers a wide range of the different types of eyewear from retro eyeglasses to popular models; and novelty contact lenses and sunglasses. We sell eyeglasses for both men and women, and even for kids. We also have accessories for your glasses such as cases and repair kits, and top quality designer eyeglass frames for fashion conscious individuals. Store owner Shelly Struthers, is a part-time model who enjoys collecting fashion items like bags, shoes, accessories, and eyewear. She always keeps up with the latest trends and and constantly updates her wardrobe with simple yet versatile and chic designs. Shelly loves wearing black and matches them with her eyeglasses collection. She is also fond of collecting fashion magazines together with novels and books as she also loves to read. Shelly aims to become a famous designer someday and launch her own line of clothing and fashion apparel.
